Version 2.4:
- [+] 5 Sep 2007, Alien - Improvement (0022000): The module is adapted to commercial design schemes.
- [!] 3 Aug 2007, Alien - Bug (0024002): The alignment was incorrect for products with long descriptions. Fixed.

Version 2.3:
- [!] 07 Jun 2007, Dragon - Bug (0021584): Non-existing product categories could cause an infinite loop during the attempt to display their content. Fixed.
- [+] 17 Apr 2007, Sheriff - Improvement (0017395): Now module templates are compatible with HTML 4.01 Transitional.

Version 2.2:
- [!] 20 Jun 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0008554): The PHP code was corrected to avoid inconsistency between the module and LiteCommerce version 2.2 (A customer could not view the contents of a category).
- [!] 03 Mar 2006, Osipov - Bug (0006031): When ShowcaseOrganizer was enabled, and one activated LayoutOrganizer, all disabled modules were spontaneously activated. Fixed.

Version 2.1:
- [!] 26 Jul 2005, Sheriff - Bug (0003609): There was an incompatibility between ProductAdviser and LayoutOrganizer modules. Fixed (templates were modified to make them compatible with "ProductAdviser" module).
